ed multi-platform OAuth authentication with strict logging and PayPal webhook integration for license generation. Developed a Telegram Bot with automated signal delivery, license validation, and cron job scheduling for 24/7 market monitoring.\"}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.h3,{id:\"full-stack-developer--freelance--nemm-technologies\",children:\"Full Stack Developer | Freelance \\u2014 nemm Technologies\"}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.p,{children:(0,n.jsx)(e.strong,{children:\"2023 - Present\"})}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.p,{children:\"Delivered 15+ client projects including Auto-Trader, ZimFlix, and Masvingo TechHub specializing in fintech, e-commerce, and community platforms. Developed a School Records Management System with licensing capabilities generating recurring revenue from educational institutions. Built ZimConnect, a community platform, and ZimBlog, a client news aggregation system with modern UI/UX.\"}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.h2,{id:\"education\",children:\"Education\"}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.h3,{id:\"o-level-education\",children:\"O-Level Education\"}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.p,{children:(0,n.jsx)(e.strong,{children:\"Completed\"})}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.p,{children:\"6 O-Level passes including Shona (A), English (B), Agriculture (B), and Sciences. Currently resitting Mathematics to align with technical expertise.\"}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.h3,{id:\"ibm-online-learning\",children:\"IBM Online Learning\"}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.p,{children:(0,n.jsx)(e.strong,{children:\"Completed\"})}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.p,{children:\"Completed IBM online programs focusing on AI, cloud computing, data science, and enterprise development. Gained practical experience beyond formal certification.\"}),`\n`,`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.h2,{id:\"technical-skills\",children:\"Technical Skills\"}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.h3,{id:\"full-stack\",children:\"Full Stack\"}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.p,{children:\"Next.js, React, TypeScript, Python, Kotlin, Java, HTML, CSS, Framer Motion\"}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.h3,{id:\"specializations\",children:\"Specializations\"}),`\n`,(0,n.j